    <div class="pdp__lead"><p>A miniature wishing well of driftwood, hand-built in Nepal, with a wooden roof and tiny bucket on a rope. The classic fairy-garden gathering spot — fairies draw water, woodland creatures stop for a drink, children whisper their wishes into the bucket.</p></div>
